            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve the <strong>Kallo chicken stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> and <strong>Sriracha hot chilli sauce</strong> in 500ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [1L]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your<strong> spicy ramen base</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>spicy ramen base</strong> to a pot over a very-low heat and cook for 5-6 min or until warmed through</p><p>Re-boil a kettle</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2251-Step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
